Natural Language Processing (NLP)
Two main parts:

NLU – Natural Language Understanding

NLG – Natural Language Generation

Core tasks:

Tokenization

Stopword removal

Stemming & Lemmatization

Part-of-Speech (POS) tagging

Named Entity Recognition (NER)

Text classification

Sentiment analysis

Summarization

Libraries & Tools

NLTK

spaCy

Gensim

Stanford NLP (Stanza)

Hugging Face Transformers

